## Summary
This documentation page explains how to effectively use Amplitude's Funnel Analysis chart to track user conversion through sequential steps in a product, helping identify drop-off points and improve engagement. It covers funnel design considerations including event selection, ordering modes (This Order, Any Order, Exact Order), conversion windows, and how to leverage insights with features like Pathfinder, Compass, and Microscope.

